videos.description: Mikal Bridges hits a 3-pointer at the start of the game then throws down an easy two-handed slam on the next possession.
videos.headline: Bridges scores first 5 points for Nova

videos.description: After a nice series of passes by Nova, Eric Paschall gets it and knocks one in from deep as the shot clock expires in the first half against Butler.
videos.headline: Paschall hits triple at shot clock buzzer

videos.description: Phil Booth takes his time, pulls up and hits a triple from the top of the key at the end of the first half to extend Villanova's lead to 44-25 over Butler.
videos.headline: Booth scores smooth 3 at the buzzer

videos.description: Donte DiVincenzo goes to the ground and almost loses the ball but he somehow finds Mikal Bridges on the outside for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bridges hits triple after near turnover

videos.description: Villanova's Collin Gillespie finds Eric Paschall who speeds inside and lays it in for a nice basket in the second half.
videos.headline: Paschall gets open for easy layup
